# CLI

Filecoindot Command Line Interface.

## Installation

```
cargo +nightly install --git https://github.com/ChainSafe/filecoindot --branch main  filecoindot-cli
```

## Usage

Verifying a proof against a CID
```
filecoindot-cli \
--cid bafy2bzaceashznt6nk5rtr7gwvsnngsnhzwrcclycxgw6ztaezh3vffsnzcis \
--proof 
```
